@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Shipping & Returns";
    ViewData["MetaDescription"] = "Wonder Watch shipping, delivery, and returns policy. Every acquisition is delivered with white-glove service and complete discretion across India.";
}

<section class="pt-[136px] pb-[96px] px-[32px] md:px-[64px] max-w-4xl mx-auto">

    <div class="mb-[64px] border-b border-white-faint pb-[48px]">
        <span class="font-sans font-bold text-[10px] text-gold tracking-[3.3px] uppercase mb-[16px] block">Client Services</span>
        <h1 class="font-serif text-[48px] md:text-[64px] text-parchment leading-none tracking-[-1.5px] mb-[16px]">Shipping &amp; Returns</h1>
        <p class="font-sans text-[14px] text-muted">Every acquisition is handled with the gravity it deserves.</p>
    </div>

    <!-- KEY METRICS STRIP -->
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-[1px] bg-white-faint mb-[80px]">
        <div class="bg-surface py-[32px] px-[24px] text-center">
            <span class="font-serif text-[40px] text-gold tracking-[-1px] block mb-[8px]">3–5</span>
            <span class="font-sans font-bold text-[10px] text-parchment tracking-[2px] uppercase">Business Days<br/>Standard Delivery</span>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-surface py-[32px] px-[24px] text-center">
            <span class="font-sans font-bold text-[32px] text-gold tracking-[-1px] block mb-[8px]">₹0</span>
            <span class="font-sans font-bold text-[10px] text-parchment tracking-[2px] uppercase">Shipping on All<br/>Acquisitions</span>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-surface py-[32px] px-[24px] text-center">
            <span class="font-serif text-[40px] text-gold tracking-[-1px] block mb-[8px]">7</span>
            <span class="font-sans font-bold text-[10px] text-parchment tracking-[2px] uppercase">Day Return<br/>Window</span>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="flex flex-col gap-[48px] font-sans text-[15px] text-muted leading-[1.75]">

        <div class="border-t border-gold-faint pt-[32px]">
            <h2 class="font-serif text-[24px] text-parchment mb-[16px]">Delivery Method</h2>
            <p class="mb-[12px]">All Wonder Watch acquisitions are shipped via our partner insured courier — fully covered against loss, damage, or theft for the declared value of the timepiece. Our logistics team handles customs documentation and ensures complete discretion in packaging.</p>
            <ul class="list-none flex flex-col gap-[8px] mt-[16px]">
                <li class="flex items-start gap-[12px]"><span class="text-gold mt-[4px]">—</span><span><strong class="text-parchment">Standard (3–5 business days):</strong> Complimentary on all orders</span></li>
                <li class="flex items-start gap-[12px]"><span class="text-gold mt-[4px]">—</span><span><strong class="text-parchment">Express (1–2 business days):</strong> Available on request for select metropolitan areas</span></li>
                <li class="flex items-start gap-[12px]"><span class="text-gold mt-[4px]">—</span><span><strong class="text-parchment">White Glove (same-day, Mumbai):</strong> Personal hand-delivery for Platinum tier members</span></li>
            </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="border-t border-gold-faint pt-[32px]">
            <h2 class="font-serif text-[24px] text-parchment mb-[16px]">Packaging</h2>
            <p>Every timepiece ships in its original manufacturer case (where available) within a matte black Wonder Watch outer box sealed with our wax emblem. A signed certificate of authenticity and white-glove delivery cloth accompany every order. Signature is required upon receipt.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="border-t border-gold-faint pt-[32px]">
            <h2 class="font-serif text-[24px] text-parchment mb-[16px]">Pan-India Coverage</h2>
            <p>We ship to all major cities and pin codes across India. Remote pin codes may require an additional 1–2 business days. International shipping is available for Platinum tier members by special arrangement — please contact our concierge for details.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="border-t border-gold-faint pt-[32px]">
            <h2 class="font-serif text-[24px] text-parchment mb-[16px]">Returns Policy</h2>
            <p class="mb-[16px]">We accept returns within <strong class="text-parchment">7 calendar days</strong> of delivery, provided:</p>
            <ul class="list-none flex flex-col gap-[8px]">
                <li class="flex items-start gap-[12px]"><span class="text-gold mt-[4px]">—</span><span>The timepiece is in its original, unworn condition</span></li>
                <li class="flex items-start gap-[12px]"><span class="text-gold mt-[4px]">—</span><span>All tags, paperwork, and packaging materials are intact</span></li>
                <li class="flex items-start gap-[12px]"><span class="text-gold mt-[4px]">—</span><span>The piece has not been serviced, resized, or modified</span></li>
            </ul>
            <p class="mt-[16px]">To initiate a return, log in to your Vault and navigate to Orders, or contact our concierge directly. We will arrange collection at our expense for eligible returns.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="border-t border-gold-faint pt-[32px]">
            <h2 class="font-serif text-[24px] text-parchment mb-[16px]">Refund Process</h2>
            <p>Upon successful inspection of the returned piece, refunds are processed within <strong class="text-parchment">5–7 business days</strong> to the original payment method. You will receive a confirmation email once the refund is initiated.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="border-t border-gold-faint pt-[32px]">
            <h2 class="font-serif text-[24px] text-parchment mb-[16px]">Questions?</h2>
            <p>Our concierge team is available six days a week. <a href="/contact" class="text-gold hover:text-parchment transition-colors">Contact us</a> or call +91 80000 00000 (Mon–Sat, 10:00–20:00 IST).</p>
        </div>

    </div>

</section>
